Pathfinding edge cases

Server tick limitations

Unexpected interactions with existing systems

---

# Development Philosophy

Keep the core RuneScape mechanics intact while layering automation on top.

This preserves the underlying gameplay simulation while enabling experimentation with automation and management gameplay.

